data.description: This charming cottage style single story 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage home is centrally located near schools, shopping, parks, freeway access, and more. Enjoy entertaining guests & family in this open floorplan - snuggle up next to the living room fireplace, play games or have a dinner party in the large dining room.  The covered patio which opens up to the HUUGE backyard is perfect for your morning coffee. Bring your imagination and create your own backyard oasis in this massive 9583 sq ft lot! Large enough for a pool, garden, play area, gazebo etc.
